Still not over my stay at @thelegacy_by_themachan in Mandawa 😍
Imagine waking up in a place where every wall has a story, where the breeze carries whispers of the past, and time slows down just enough for you to soak it all in. From the moment I walked through those vintage wooden doors, I felt like I had stepped into a living piece of history. The faded frescoes, the creaking floors, the cozy courtyards—it all felt so real, so raw, so beautiful.
What made it even more special? The people. The warmth, the food , the hospitality 🫰
If you’re ever in Mandawa and looking for a stay that feels, not just looks, like heritage— @thelegacy_by_themachan is it. 
Can’t wait to be back. 💛
